{
  "stem": "13395.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No matter how bad it is, there's always somewhere, sometime where you have to, to look at the lighter side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- in our rations, there was so many grams of jam that you would be given.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the merchant already would take out some of the jam and put water in because it went by weight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he sold the jam on the black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We, of course, didn't have money to buy anything on the black market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when he gave-- sold you your ration of jam, that was already watered down a little.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I was growing up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was 14, 15, 16.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was craving for sweet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the only thing we had was this jam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when my mother wouldn't be home, I would take a spoon of jam and put a spoon of water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the more jam I took out and the more water I put in, it became slowly juice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I thought my mother will never notice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then-- and she was saving the jam for the holidays because she wanted to bring some normalcy into our lives.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For instance, we had a Seder in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had services for Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur in our room where we had people come, and it all clandestine because we were not allowed to congregate more than two, three people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we had prayers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a Torah scroll was brought in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had services for yontif.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my mother was saving the jam to bake a cake.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when she made the dough-- and she's now taking the jar with the jam, and she finds there is nothing-- no jam, but just some red juice.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She threw the jar at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But she didn't hit me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She hit the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
